These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, domino, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy, spy, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
House: craftsman, cottage, colonial, tower
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person playing scrabble##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the cottage house##1
3. the fan of r&b is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is the craftsman house##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the colonial house##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game         | scrabble  | bridge  | snooker | domino |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy | scientific | satire  | spy  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| House           | craftsman          | cottage     | colonial    | tower     |

