.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, townhouse, craftsman
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dunhill, game, blend
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, drawing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the game-smoker is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House      | townhouse     | farmhouse       | cape-cod | craftsman        |
| Cigar          | blend     | dunhill       | game   | siglo   |
| Hobby   | drawing      | rock-climbing       | hiking     | cooking    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

