.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dannemann, chaman, bongani
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, skateboard, tram, helicopter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, cottage, craftsman
 1. the bongani-smoker is the craftsman house##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Cigar      | dannemann | fonseca       | bongani        | chaman        |
| Transport           | skateboard   | tram | train   | helicopter |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| House           | cottage         | gothic-revival  | craftsman       | futuristic         |

