.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
City: prague, boston, venice, miami
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, poker, chess
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, artichoke, cabbage, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| City           | boston   | prague  | miami | venice |
| Game   | poker | chess       | mah-jongg       | backgammon     |
| Food   | cabbage       | cauliflower    | artichoke     | cranberry  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

