The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, subway, jet-ski
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, mauve, red
1. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes red is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Birthday           | october  | january    | july | june |
| Transport   | subway      | motorbike    | scooter         | jet-ski    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Color         | fuchsia | blood-red | red      | mauve      |

