 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person who growsrose is the person who likes red##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | banana  | pomegranate | orange     | blueberry |
| Color           | amber  | red      | blood-red | ebony    |
