4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, mah-jongg, monopoly
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, lacrosse, ice-hockey
 1. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 3. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of disco##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | reggae | disco     | indie    | trance |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Game         | poker   | mah-jongg  | monopoly        | backgammon    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | handball | climbing    | lacrosse |

